TextEng: <StartAction>[Give him the pass]</Start> Here you go.
<StartCheck>[Threaten]</Start> You dare question me?!
Does the tower inform you of all their guests?
You will let me in before I grow... angry.
Fine, I'll just kill you now.
<StartCheck>[Threaten]</Start> You questions me?!
Wizards tell you 'bout all guests, huh?
You lets me in or me gets very mad!
Text: 너 나 들여보내든지 나 엄청 화나!

TextEng: Okays, me kills you now.
<StartCheck>[Lie]</Start> I am the Mulhorandi ambassador, I assure you.
<StartCheck>[Lie]</Start> Me Mulhorandi ambassador, me assures you, okays?
Are you refusing me entry?
You saying me cannot go in?
Text: 너 나 못 들어간다고 하는 거야?

TextEng: That's it. You're a dead man.
That it. You dead man, now.
Maybe you shoulds ask wizards, huh?
Perhaps you should ask your wizards, then.
Goodbye.
Good. You dies, now.
Me has questions.
Excellent. Now you die.
I have some questions.
Tells me 'bout tower.
Why is so much security?
You talks 'bout fighting...?
Who this new Archmage guy?
Tell me about the Host Tower.
Just how big is tower?
You hears 'bout someone named Maugrim?
You knows 'bout cult in tower, maybe?
Text: 너 탑에 사교 있다는 거 알아?

TextEng: Just how large is the tower?
Have you heard of someone named Maugrim?
Do you know about any cult in the tower?
Text: 탑에 사교가 있다는 건 알고 있나요?

TextEng: Why all the tight security?
You mentioned fighting...?
What you means by mess?
What do you mean by a mess?
Who is this new Archmage Arcane?
Old archmage dead, huh?
The former Archmage is dead?
